HEADWORD: Cornaceae
<hw>Cornaceae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a natural family of trees
including the genera <gen>Aucuba</gen>; <gen>Cornus</gen>;
<gen>Corokia</gen>; <gen>Curtisia</gen>; <gen>Griselinia</gen>; and
<gen>Helwingia</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Cornaceae</fam>, dogwood
family.</syn>⟦br⟧
